":"2019-10-19T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"班紅官唔會理 因為佢地眼中香港人唔係人<br />\n<br />\n《不屈進行曲》 《March of the Indomitable》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ryqGOGig_AI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FryqGOGig_AI&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=7d7d1c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ryqGOGig_AI</a>"},{"pid":"e9f94236549f2c1e3555e63af97b5e3cc613695b","tid":1663534,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"即係只要係政府啲人<br />\n就算做左咩都唔洗負責任<br />\n身分亦唔洗被人知<br />\n要攞no. 就欠奉<br />\n要投掓去相關部門<br />\n佢又話可以自證身份但又唔洗出樣<br />\n<br />\n咁普通市民點認證<br />\n而家重未計某一日喺地鐵站有班市民好似被警察暴力襲擊打過，第時又要保護佢地又唔出no.？<br />\n<br />\n香港政府到底係要嚟做咩<br />\n呢幾個月就係負責屈市民打市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n定係負責對市民生活造成不便"},{"pid":"f82cc51536881685d82641058b6a44fcafedfbf3","tid":1663534,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"諗諗下<br />\n第日人大釋法話當初搞錯左<br />\n其實係想寫「五十年不便」<br />\n都係一個讀音啫<br />\n邊係釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d18f26dd327b0cb46f0f152a91b405a629e7a5d","tid":1663534,"uid":249252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"鳩拉就叻<br />\n開名就縮<br />\n正一撚樣"},{"pid":"da72c17e4b5943534628381ebca2720050db0bc2","tid":1663534,"uid":128603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"覺得份工唔見得光就咪做啦。"},{"pid":"00110dac84729bece64a9f951b9d47db6faaacf4","tid":1663534,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"on9 黑警"},{"pid":"f28651c3f526c8d8d01624a444b0b616caeba330","tid":1663534,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"可能只是穿上警服， 卻不是香港人， 別為難他們吧......"},{"pid":"a73429ced9182534864c5eb90257d670eaaa25c8","tid":1663534,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0